snippet.textDisplay:
THIS IS LONG AS FUCK AND IF YOU NOT OF FAN OF DUDE SINCE WAY BACK JUST SKIP THIS COMMENT BUT IF YOU KNOW, YOU KNOW.




People got this shit all wrong, im the nigga from back when Kissland dropped who broke down the story on that years ago I got yall again here(Kissland my fav album from Abel btw its too good and underrated and yes I mean above even Trilogy even tho it isn't an official album)


These lil small things in the video are fucking great but you have to really pay attention to catch some of the things in here if you're just looking and not listening and looking at the same time it won't even make sense. Not only that but you have to go back to the two videos before this to know wtf is going on.....the are all linked per album he does this btw like most of his videos even since Kissland which is how i learned the fucking story for Kissland but enough of that lets get it.




So lets go back to the beginning of whats happening, Abel has been doing all kinds of shit in these videos....most of it just wild reckless shit but the Dark shit doesn't start happening until about halfway through the video for Heartless which is the first video of course and its when he licks the toad where he starts seeing the plant or whatever that is form after the hallucinogen takes effect he see's it in this video too but I'll get back to that. For the people who don't know why his nose is fucked up the bouncers in the strip club fucked him up on blinding lights towards the end for most likely getting too friendly with the girl on stage even called the cops and he got away to do what you ask? you guessed it more wild shit idk why he's doing it but it is what its he's Abel so we just gonna let it slide and charge it to the game. Something happens to him at certain times it seems literally, idk if its when he took the drug or just a certain time in general...probably around Midnight which would make sense because in this video here he's leaving Jimmy Kimmel show which goes on from like 11pm to like midnight i think? I don't watch so I don't know the exact times but we talking westcoast times and thats where im from so I know thats when its on around that time...he leaves it and he instantly changes his face after leaving knowing some bad shit is about to happen he keeps checking his back and the red lights are a sign of it coming. He keeps seeing them walking through the tunnel every one he passes his smile fades more and more....




Alrighty folks first time stamp, 1:12 you hear a snippet of what i assume is a track from the album start playing this is sign here for what ever he turns into is coming and its coming soon its not Abel its something else idk wtf he is but the shit is not right i'll just say that....the music fades out and it zooms in on his eyes, as it fades out so we know its still him as himself he feels pain he goes quickly for the nose that got fucked up while I'll just call him "the other guy" was doing what he does in that club. The significance of it zooming is on his eyes is in the Heartless video when he first licks the toad, his eyes completely change into a cat like pupil, and thus the other guy knows he has to hide that from the sight of what seems to be the women he's goes after thats not the only reason though....but what does the other guy do? he always has the glasses on and does even more wild shit than regular Abel. Walking into the alley way where the AFTER HOURS pops up Abel is looking around as if someone is watching him not knowing that whatever he's afraid of isn't following him at all, its inside of him already the time in which he turns into the other guy is upon us the video is letting us know at this point that this is around the time it starts happening.The other guy is almost here and It's a demonic like thing for sure though and it was manifested into him by someone else other than himself even though he himself did decide to lick the toad not knowing what he was getting himself into (you can check on 3:16 of the heartless video if ya don't believe me).


Right after that alley scene he's walking in the subway and what do we hear? its another snippet shit aint looking good chief, ima tell you now as soon as it stops Abel hears some shit in the background and turns around isntantly mans know something going on and whats happening i mean shit as soon as he hits the bottom of the escalator he got that look his face as if he in the line at walmart and the lady in front of him got 2 baskets full of shit and she paying in coins yeah its looking cryptic for our boy man but this calls for the second time stamp.....




2:35 Music starts playing, this time its two songs.....the ending of after hours and another unreleased album track most likely, he can feel it coming at this point he knows that knows the time and he's tired of fighting it we havent seen him make this face since he left the tunnel of the Kimmel Show those were the last time he had encountered the red lights too....at this point he is looking for a way out of it but he just can't find a way with his face getting more and more intense then finally at 3:14 the camera pans down at his gloves dude is here a and he's ready he's getting the same bumps he got on his hand on heartless( at around on that video 3:00 i want to say)...he just screams as his body is becoming out of his control dudes really trying to fight becoming the other guy but its time as soon as he walks a few more steps the red light is there and its done...he just looks up into the light and turns into the other guy, and he puts the glasses on immediately....wanna know why its not to hide it from the people around him there are no women around him....its because the other guy is the one whose "Blinded By The Lights", but like i said waaaaaay earlier as he's looking into the light with the glasses on what do we see?? That same plant we saw when he first licked the toad but in different colors red and a white one flickering the white one is abel im guessing the red one is the other guy you can see a very small glimpse of it at the very beginning of this video in his eye. Since there conflicting and Abel is trying to keep control the other guy is literally dragging him to the nearest female im guessing he eats them or their hearts or something them which would explain why at the very begging of blinding lights he has a lot of blood around and in his mouth....and for those that don't know that beginning is after everything in blinding lights happens, as you can see he already had the cut on his nose at the beginning and he has a short flash of the girl who was singing on stage at the end thus making her his prey. I'm sure the other guy just looks into what Abel him self is doing and trys to either take who Abel loves and devour them or if he's hungry and desperate he'll just take whatever he can get for the time being.




Thus going to when he's being pulled by what seems to be nothing.....its the other guy needing to have something, absolutely anything in fact no matter whose there and who she is he's making Abel go to whatever is close and getting him to where he needs to be in order to get what he needs, now we go to 4:13 the music has been playing this whole time that the other guy has been out in this short film in particular.....it goes back to the ending of after hours because the other guy is about to get what he wants and we know what that is now and its the heart of a woman he wants to devour it he's there waiting in full control just standing there calmly, as the door closes i imagine the guy has been dealt with swiftly bro u don't hear shit from him...but the girl she is screaming I guess this dude is devouring hearts of women while they are still alive man which would be like a way of him saying, he really destroys the trust, love, and attention he gives to these women and will say things to get what he wants from them which is their trust and hearts by doing and saying what he needs to in order for them to let their guards down to make it happen. He literally is doing it in the song After Hours itself..




he is telling us in the song titles everything in the story thats the other guy is about.....he's Heartless, Blinded By the Lights, and he comes out After Hours I know its not finished but I mean this is what I got for now and goddamn is it fun watching this guy do all this shit






TLDR; Abel is being controlled by a split personality of himself who is a womanizing, crazy, self centered guy who doesn't care about he just want what he wan'ts and that guy was born because of drugs taken before....but now continuously comes out despite trying to fight it by just simply a certain time within a day approaching. He will say anything in order for his fantasies and desires to be fulfilled. He hides it in a metaphorical sense in the videos with Glasses and the gloves, but the real him has to hide it with a smile. But in the words of Abel himself, when he's fucked up that's the real him so I'm just excited to see how this all plays out....does Abel give in during the rest of the album? or does he try to fight this?


Sorry for the long ass post but its been a while since I been this excited about one of his projects


Pce. :]

snippet.textDisplay: I've never commented on a YouTube video but i just wanted to say my interpretation. I think that this is backwards. He has a flashback at 1:06 and you can hear the screams from the elevator. This starts with the elevator scene since he's reminiscing about it and he's dragged back to the spotlight to perform, execute and put a fake smile on his face but he's unhappy w himself. Hence all the scars. He only has the scar on his nose in the elevator but goes to the show w multiple, probably after the struggle. Idk what the couple represents? The idea of love? Not being happy? But it's all symbolism. I'm not sure what the glasses mean and the lights/ flower? Maybe a facade? His alter ego? It's like he loses himself or becomes a totally different person. He's trying to run away from who he is but it's pulling him back. He's going through an episode and trying to keep his composure together but the bad guy always comes back no matter how much he puts him in the back of his subconscious. He's tryna please his fans but he's not happy himself, he's essentially at war with himself and he's spiraling out of control going back and forth from the good side to the bad.

snippet.textDisplay: The Weeknd is a genius on making his music videos , they all have a meaning to them. When beauty behind the madness came out, his 3 music videos “The hills” “Tell your friends” “can’t feel my face “ were of him selling his souls to the devil , and then him killing the devil. In the music video “ tell your friends” you can see him shoot the devil and in there’s a burning bush with fire which has meaning towards god and being good. in “The Hills” He crashes the car with the 2 girls. And when he walks into the house , The devil is waiting for him with the 2 girls. Which means that he is offering women if he sells his soul. In “Can’t feel my face” The Weeknd is singing at the club. But no one is paying attention to him and throw something at him to try to get him off stage. The devil is seen smoking a cigar watching him. The people continue to not want him on stage until the devil throws a lighter which sets The Weeknd on fire. Then that’s when his soul is sold to the devil and he is given what he wants. Fame and women , As soon as he is on fire. The whole club is dancing and loving him which means the fame is given to him as part of the deal with the devil.  When Starboy came out. You can see The Weeknd tie up his old self, And the New Abel. He wears a cross meaning that he is was given another chance by god to destroy his evil past and kill the Old Abel. That’s why you see The Weeknd destroy all of his awards and records because all of those were given by the Illuminati and were not earned by working hard. He is seen killing himself in most of his music videos at the end but it’s very hard to understand why he does that. Now in “Blinding lights” he is seen under the influence of hard drugs that make him hallucinate, him licking the frog is the drug and the flower he has hallucinations. Are hardcore drugs. In Heartless he is seen having very bad flashbacks and also the devil is coming after him On this video it seems like The Weeknd is going crazy and the devil is taking over his mind. That’s why at the end the elevator probably takes them to hell to sacrifice people for the deal he is going to make with the devil.

snippet.textDisplay: The Weeknd used to be homeless in Vancouver. The beginning shows him leaving the audience and cameras and then as he heads down underground its supposed to represent where he came from and how he used to live. Just wandering. Then the dragging around after he puts the glasses on is his spiral with drugs and inability to full grasp the life he has now. Then in the elevator you seem him still and looking forward to represent the face he puts on when coming around other people again..IMO
